node.text:
Five years ago, we were lucky enough to meet and celebrate 16-year-old Bretagne and her handler, Denise Corliss. Bretagne was the last surviving search and rescue dog at Ground Zero, and aided in several other disaster missions over her lifetime with Texas Task Force 1.
Her invaluable work and effort will never be forgotten, and neither will she. Thank you both for your incredible service. ❤️ , your family at BARK
.
.
.
.
#bretagne #searchandrescuedog #hero #searchandrescue #disasterrelief #texastaskforce1

node.title: We will never forget you, Bretagne ❤️
